.XI about - "Information About MicroEmacs"
.SH NAME
about \- Information About \*(mE 
.Me $a
.SH SYNOPSIS
.na
.B about
.ad
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B about
displays  information about the current \*(mE editing session and includes the
following information:-
.BS
Version number and date information for \*(mE.
.BU
Global status  information  including the number of active  buffers and global
mode status information.
.BU
Current buffer status information; buffer modes and buffer size information.
.BE 0
.SH EXAMPLE
